snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Idol Janshi Suchie-Pai Mecha Genteiban (1998)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Idol Janshi Suchie-Pai Mecha Genteiban is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Jaleco Entertainment, which was released in Japan in 1998.
